# Edge Cases and Error Handling Tests

Test error conditions and edge cases.

## Variables
@baseUrl = http://127.0.0.1:8000

### Test Creating Session with Invalid Backend
POST {{baseUrl}}/sessions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "backends": ["nonexistent_backend"],
  "name": "Should Fail"
}

### Test Creating Session with Empty Backends
POST {{baseUrl}}/sessions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "backends": [],
  "name": "Empty Backends"
}

### Test Creating Session with Mixed Valid/Invalid Backends
POST {{baseUrl}}/sessions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "backends": ["ollama", "fake_backend"],
  "name": "Mixed Backends"
}

